                                    <div class="muscle-item">
                                        <div class="muscle-img">
                                            <img src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Biceps-Short-Head-.png" alt="">
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="has-medium-font-size">Biceps Short Head </p>
                                        <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Most inside portion of the biceps. Located at the front of your upper arm closest to your chest.</p></p>
                                    </div>
